data.description: Don’t miss the opportunity to make this wonderful charming home yours. Filled with natural light the living area opens into the dining area and kitchen. The Kitchen boasts updated cabinets & hardware, plenty of counter space along with a coffee bar. The Refrigerator remains with the home. The roof is around 3 years old and HVAC is 2017. No carpet. The Dining area overlooks the backyard which features a large deck and a treehouse for your outdoor gatherings. This home is nestled in a peaceful neighborhood and offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Located near shopping, dining, school, and parks. This home is ready for its next owners. Schedule a showing today and image the possibilities. This property may qualify for a $5000 Chase Homebuyer Grant that can be used to reduce the cost. Seller is motivated.
